Plans & Billing
===============

Sign up for a [monthly plan](https://www.cognitoforms.com/pricing) and take your forms to the next level. You can upgrade or downgrade your subscription at any time for any reason. When downgrading, a prorated amount for the time remaining in the current month will be credited back to your account. These credits will be automatically applied to future subscription payments. See our [terms of service](https://www.cognitoforms.com/legal/3/terms-of-service#payment) for additional information.

Entries above the monthly limit will be unavailable until you upgrade to the appropriate plan level. Files that exceed your storage capacity will be captured, but all files will be unavailable until you upgrade to a plan level with sufficient storage. Learn more about your organization’s [usage limits](https://www.cognitoforms.com/support/153/account-organizations/organization-management/checking-usage).
